             was indicted for <rs id="t18060917-73-off395" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18060917-73-off395" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18060917-73-off395" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18060917-73-cd396" type="crimeDate">9th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060917-73-off395 t18060917-73-cd396"></join>, fifty yards of linen, value 8 l. twenty-four dozen of shirt buttons, value 5 s. two ounces of sewing silk, value 4 s. four yards of cambric, value 1 l. 10 s. and thirty-six yards of silk cord, value 2 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18060917-73-victim694" type="victimName">
                        Christopher 
                        Wilson
                     <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim694" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim694" type="given" value="Christopher"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim694" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , 
                     
                        <persName id="t18060917-73-victim696" type="victimName">
                           Henry 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim696" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim696" type="given" value="Henry"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim696" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , 
                     
                        <persName id="t18060917-73-victim698" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Wilson
                        <interp inst="t18060917-73-victim698" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
